{"tid":806083,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"［smartone］屋企上唔到網求救","createTime":"2018-09-04T11:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T11:17:37.000Z","uid":181406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c821dad899b790dfbdb49974d8a9435488f0d81a","tid":806083,"uid":181406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"我唔將光纖寬頻條GE1線連落router佢係著咗三盞燈嘅，但係我將佢連返落router個光纖盒佢就restart跟住一路停咗喺第一盞燈，究竟係乜事？求高手<br />\n<br />\n無將條GE1線插落router係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/191426_a8bb7ccf0b712f6000a24b9cf3a3e892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F191426_a8bb7ccf0b712f6000a24b9cf3a3e892.png&h=625aa285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n插咗入router就邊咗咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/191509_f9eedb287d5788bf33677ff27a9be124.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F191509_f9eedb287d5788bf33677ff27a9be124.png&h=8edfa3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾日打咗俾smartone問，佢話叫師傅上黎整，點知唔知點解前日自己上得返，就個師傅講唔洗上黎，但係今日又黎過，真係求救，無上網好慘，手機數據唔係無限"}]}